{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875129596,"sessionID":"ses_285982822ffevXkXdO724q4nnA","part":{"id":"prt_d7a67fc200017WsLQOdJhnKuMI","messageID":"msg_d7a67e8d0001b1Yy3ZJcJPj5pU","sessionID":"ses_285982822ffevXkXdO724q4nnA","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_442780568edd4ab7bd182655","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n2: \n3: **Module:** docker  \n4: **Language:** Dockerfile  \n5: **Size:** S  \n6: **Design Stage:** ST-3 completed\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Phase 1: Directory & Base Dockerfile\n11: \n12: - [ ] **T001** Create `docker/` directory at project root\n13: - [ ] **T002** Create `docker/base.Dockerfile` with Go build environment\n14:   - Base image: `golang:1.24-alpine`\n15:   - Include go mod download\n16:   - Build stage named: `builder`\n17: - [ ] **T003** Add build arguments to base.Dockerfile (GO_VERSION, BUILDER_IMAGE, RUNTIME_IMAGE, BINARY_VERSION)\n18: - [ ] **T004** Verify `docker build -f docker/base.Dockerfile --target builder -t agentcube-builder:test .` succeeds\n19: \n20: ---\n21: \n22: ## Phase 2: Router Dockerfile\n23: \n24: - [ ] **T010** Create `docker/Dockerfile.router` with multi-stage build\n25: - [ ] **T011** Builder stage copies source and builds router binary from `cmd/router/main.go`\n26: - [ ] **T012** Runtime stage uses `alpine:3.19` as base\n27: - [ ] **T013** Create non-root user `agentcube` (UID 1000)\n28: - [ ] **T014** Copy binary from builder stage to `/usr/local/bin/router`\n29: - [ ] **T015** Set correct file permissions (chmod +x)\n30: - [ ] **T016** Configure ENTRYPOINT for router binary\n31: - [ ] **T017** Verify `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-router:test .` succeeds\n32: \n33: ---\n34: \n35: ## Phase 3: Workload Manager Dockerfile\n36: \n37: - [ ] **T020** Create `docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager` with multi-stage build\n38: - [ ] **T021** Builder stage builds workload-manager binary from `cmd/workload-manager/main.go`\n39: - [ ] **T022** Runtime stage uses `alpine:3.19` as base\n40: - [ ] **T023** Create non-root user `agentcube` (UID 1000)\n41: - [ ] **T024** Copy binary from builder stage to `/usr/local/bin/workload-manager`\n42: - [ ] **T025** Set correct file permissions (chmod +x)\n43: - [ ] **T026** Configure ENTRYPOINT for workload-manager binary\n44: - [ ] **T027** Verify `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager -t agentcube-workload-manager:test .` succeeds\n45: \n46: ---\n47: \n48: ## Phase 4: Agentd Dockerfile\n49: \n50: - [ ] **T030** Create `docker/Dockerfile.agentd` with multi-stage build\n51: - [ ] **T031** Builder stage builds agentd binary from `cmd/agentd/main.go`\n52: - [ ] **T032** Builder stage builds picod binary from `cmd/picod/main.go`\n53: - [ ] **T033** Runtime stage uses `alpine:3.19` as base\n54: - [ ] **T034** Create non-root user `agentcube` (UID 1000)\n55: - [ ] **T035** Copy both binaries from builder stage to `/usr/local/bin/`\n56: - [ ] **T036** Set correct file permissions (chmod +x)\n57: - [ ] **T037** Configure ENTRYPOINT for agentd binary (supports picod as argument)\n58: - [ ] **T038** Verify `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.agentd -t agentcube-agentd:test .` succeeds\n59: \n60: ---\n61: \n62: ## Phase 5: Binary Execution Verification\n63: \n64: - [ ] **T040** Test router binary: `docker run --rm agentcube-router:test --help` exits 0\n65: - [ ] **T041** Test workload-manager binary: `docker run --rm agentcube-workload-manager:test --help` exits 0\n66: - [ ] **T042** Test agentd binary: `docker run --rm agentcube-agentd:test --help` exits 0\n67: - [ ] **T043** Test picod binary: `docker run --rm agentcube-agentd:test picod --help` exits 0\n68: - [ ] **T044** Test router version: `docker run --rm agentcube-router:test version` exits 0\n69: \n70: ---\n71: \n72: ## Phase 6: Security Verification\n73: \n74: - [ ] **T050** Verify router runs as non-root: `docker run --rm agentcube-router:id` shows uid=1000\n75: - [ ] **T051** Verify workload-manager runs as non-root: `docker run --rm agentcube-workload-manager:id` shows uid=1000\n76: - [ ] **T052** Verify agentd runs as non-root: `docker run --rm agentcube-agentd:id` shows uid=1000\n77: - [ ] **T053** Verify no source code in router: `docker run --rm agentcube-router ls /build` returns error\n78: - [ ] **T054** Verify no go.mod in router: `docker run --rm agentcube-router cat go.mod` returns error\n79: \n80: ---\n81: \n82: ## Phase 7: Image Size Verification\n83: \n84: - [ ] **T060** Check router image size: `docker images agentcube-router --format \"{{.Size}}\"` < 50MB\n85: - [ ] **T061** Check workload-manager image size: `docker images agentcube-workload-manager --format \"{{.Size}}\"` < 50MB\n86: - [ ] **T062** Check agentd image size: `docker images agentcube-agentd --format \"{{.Size}}\"` < 60MB\n87: \n88: ---\n89: \n90: ## Phase 8: Makefile Integration (Optional)\n91: \n92: - [ ] **T070** Add docker-build-router target to Makefile\n93: - [ ] **T071** Add docker-build-workload-manager target to Makefile\n94: - [ ] **T072** Add docker-build-agentd target to Makefile\n95: - [ ] **T073** Add docker-build (all) target to Makefile\n96: - [ ] **T074** Verify `make docker-build-router` succeeds\n97: \n98: ---\n99: \n100: ## Phase 9: Cache Reuse Verification\n101: \n102: - [ ] **T080** Run first build (cold): `time docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-router:test .`\n103: - [ ] **T081** Run second build (no changes): `time docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-router:test .`\n104: - [ ] **T082** Verify second build completes in < 30 seconds (cache reused)\n105: \n106: ---\n107: \n108: ## Dependencies\n109: \n110: ```\n111: T001 → T002 → T003 → T004\n112: T010-T017 (Router - depends on T002-T004)\n113: T020-T027 (Workload Manager - depends on T002-T004)\n114: T030-T038 (Agentd - depends on T002-T004)\n115: T040-T044 (Binary tests - depends on T017, T027, T038)\n116: T050-T054 (Security tests - depends on T040-T044)\n117: T060-T062 (Size tests - depends on T040-T044)\n118: T070-T074 (Makefile - can parallel after T040-T044)\n119: T080-T082 (Cache tests - depends on T017)\n120: ```\n121: \n122: **Parallel:** Phase 2, 3, 4 (Router, Workload Manager, Agentd Dockerfiles) can be done in parallel after Phase 1\n123: \n124: ## Acceptance Criteria\n125: \n126: - [ ] `docker/base.Dockerfile` exists with Go builder stage\n127: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile.router` builds successfully, image < 50MB\n128: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager` builds successfully, image < 50MB\n129: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile.agentd` builds successfully, image < 60MB\n130: - [ ] All binaries execute correctly inside containers\n131: - [ ] All containers run as non-root (uid=1000)\n132: - [ ] No source code present in runtime images\n133: - [ ] Build cache works correctly (second build < 30s)\n134: \n135: ## Verification Commands\n136: \n137: ```bash\n138: # Build all images\n139: docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-router:latest .\n140: docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager -t agentcube-workload-manager:latest .\n141: docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.agentd -t agentcube-agentd:latest .\n142: \n143: # Binary verification\n144: docker run --rm agentcube-router version\n145: docker run --rm agentcube-workload-manager --help\n146: docker run --rm agentcube-agentd --help\n147: docker run --rm agentcube-agentd picod --help\n148: \n149: # Security verification\n150: docker run --rm agentcube-router id\n151: docker run --rm agentcube-router ls /build\n152: \n153: # Size verification\n154: docker images agentcube-router\n155: docker images agentcube-workload-manager\n156: docker images agentcube-agentd\n157: ```\n\n(End of file - total 157 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n\n**Module:** docker  \n**Language:** Dockerfile  \n**Size:** S  \n**Design Stage:** ST-3 completed\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Directory & Base Dockerfile\n\n- [ ] **T001** Create `docker/` directory at project root\n- [ ] **T002** Create `docker/base.Dockerfile` with Go build environment\n  - Base image: `golang:1.24-alpine`\n  - Include go mod download\n  - Build stage named: `builder`\n- [ ] **T003** Add build arguments to base.Dockerfile (GO_VERSION, BUILDER_IMAGE, RUNTIME_IMAGE, BINARY_VERSION)\n- [ ] **T004** Verify `docker build -f docker/base.Dockerfile --target builder -t agentcube-builder:test .` succeeds\n\n---","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775875129574,"end":1775875129593}}}}
