{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875197460,"sessionID":"ses_285982822ffevXkXdO724q4nnA","part":{"id":"prt_d7a68f166001H5aQ195pE2ZY1P","messageID":"msg_d7a68e88c0019tyyGgiKDrdRc9","sessionID":"ses_285982822ffevXkXdO724q4nnA","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_1472c0b3ccf4450296de3d8b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# syntax=docker/dockerfile:1.4\n\n# ==============================================================================\n# AgentCube Router Dockerfile - Multi-stage Build\n# ==============================================================================\n\n# Build arguments\nARG GO_VERSION=1.24\nARG BUILDER_IMAGE=golang:${GO_VERSION}-alpine\nARG RUNTIME_IMAGE=alpine:3.19\nARG BINARY_VERSION=dev\n\n# ==============================================================================\n# Builder Stage - Go build environment\n# ==============================================================================\nFROM ${BUILDER_IMAGE} AS builder\n\n# Install build dependencies\nRUN apk add --no-cache git\n\n# Set working directory\nWORKDIR /build\n\n# Copy go mod files first for better layer caching\nCOPY go.mod go.sum ./\n\n# Download dependencies\nRUN go mod download\n\n# Copy the rest of the source code\nCOPY . .\n\n# Build arguments for binary version\nARG BINARY_VERSION\n\n# Build router binary\nRUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build \\\n    -ldflags=\"-X main.version=${BINARY_VERSION}\" \\\n    -o router ./cmd/router\n\n# ==============================================================================\n# Runtime Stage - Alpine runtime with non-root user\n# ==============================================================================\nFROM ${RUNTIME_IMAGE} AS runtime\n\n# Create non-root user\nRUN adduser -D -u 1000 agentcube\n\n# Switch to non-root user\nUSER 1000\n\n# Set working directory\nWORKDIR /home/agentcube\n\n# Copy binary from builder\nCOPY --from=builder /build/router /usr/local/bin/router\n\n# Ensure binary is executable\nRUN chmod +x /usr/local/bin/router\n\n# Set entrypoint\nENTRYPOINT [\"/usr/local/bin/router\"]","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/docker/Dockerfile.router"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler_test.go\">\nERROR [146:6] expected '(', found TestGetObservedGenerationCodeInterpreter\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/workloadmanager/expiration_test.go\">\nERROR [94:16] undefined: metav1\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go\">\nERROR [15:2] \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/watch\" imported and not used\nERROR [66:14] cannot use &metav1.Status{…} (value of type *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status) as error value in return statement: *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status does not implement error (missing method Error)\nERROR [81:9] cannot use &metav1.Status{…} (value of type *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status) as error value in return statement: *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status does not implement error (missing method Error)\nERROR [95:14] cannot use &metav1.Status{…} (value of type *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status) as error value in return statement: *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status does not implement error (missing method Error)\nERROR [109:14] cannot use &metav1.Status{…} (value of type *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status) as error value in return statement: *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/met