{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875239473,"sessionID":"ses_285982822ffevXkXdO724q4nnA","part":{"id":"prt_d7a696e2b001G3ueo2EZdmDEQC","messageID":"msg_d7a6966c9001ousObToUBTKs7l","sessionID":"ses_285982822ffevXkXdO724q4nnA","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_8a17eeb13ceb4bd880132fd9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# ==============================================================================\n# AgentCube Makefile\n# ==============================================================================\n\nDOCKER_REGISTRY ?= agentcube\nDOCKER_TAG ?= latest\nGO_VERSION ?= 1.24\nBINARY_VERSION ?= dev\n\n# ==============================================================================\n# Docker Build Targets\n# ==============================================================================\n\n.PHONY: docker-build docker-build-router docker-build-workload-manager docker-build-agentd\n.PHONY: docker-push docker-push-router docker-push-workload-manager docker-push-agentd\n.PHONY: docker-build-all validate-dockerfiles validate-images\n\n# Build all images\ndocker-build: docker-build-router docker-build-workload-manager docker-build-agentd\n\n# Build router image\ndocker-build-router:\n\tdocker build \\\n\t\t-f docker/Dockerfile.router \\\n\t\t--build-arg GO_VERSION=$(GO_VERSION) \\\n\t\t--build-arg BINARY_VERSION=$(BINARY_VERSION) \\\n\t\t-t $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-router:$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n\t\t-t $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-router:latest \\\n\t\t.\n\n# Build workload-manager image\ndocker-build-workload-manager:\n\tdocker build \\\n\t\t-f docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager \\\n\t\t--build-arg GO_VERSION=$(GO_VERSION) \\\n\t\t--build-arg BINARY_VERSION=$(BINARY_VERSION) \\\n\t\t-t $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-workload-manager:$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n\t\t-t $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-workload-manager:latest \\\n\t\t.\n\n# Build agentd image (includes picod)\ndocker-build-agentd:\n\tdocker build \\\n\t\t-f docker/Dockerfile.agentd \\\n\t\t--build-arg GO_VERSION=$(GO_VERSION) \\\n\t\t--build-arg BINARY_VERSION=$(BINARY_VERSION) \\\n\t\t-t $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-agentd:$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n\t\t-t $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-agentd:latest \\\n\t\t.\n\n# Build all images (alias)\ndocker-build-all: docker-build\n\n# ==============================================================================\n# Docker Push Targets\n# ==============================================================================\n\ndocker-push: docker-push-router docker-push-workload-manager docker-push-agentd\n\ndocker-push-router:\n\tdocker push $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-router:$(DOCKER_TAG)\n\tdocker push $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-router:latest\n\ndocker-push-workload-manager:\n\tdocker push $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-workload-manager:$(DOCKER_TAG)\n\tdocker push $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-workload-manager:latest\n\ndocker-push-agentd:\n\tdocker push $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-agentd:$(DOCKER_TAG)\n\tdocker push $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-agentd:latest\n\n# ==============================================================================\n# Validation Targets\n# ==============================================================================\n\nvalidate-dockerfiles:\n\t@echo \"Validating Dockerfiles...\"\n\t@docker build -f docker/base.Dockerfile --target builder --no-run . || (echo \"base.Dockerfile validation failed\" && exit 1)\n\t@docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router --target runtime --no-run . || (echo \"Dockerfile.router validation failed\" && exit 1)\n\t@docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager --target runtime --no-run . || (echo \"Dockerfile.workload-manager validation failed\" && exit 1)\n\t@docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.agentd --target runtime --no-run . || (echo \"Dockerfile.agentd validation failed\" && exit 1)\n\t@echo \"All Dockerfiles are valid\"\n\nvalidate-images: docker-build\n\t@echo \"Validating image binaries...\"\n\t@docker run --rm $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-router --help > /dev/null || (echo \"Router binary failed\" && exit 1)\n\t@docker run --rm $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-workload-manager --help > /dev/null || (echo \"Workload-manager binary failed\" && exit 1)\n\t@docker run --rm $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-agentd --help > /dev/null || (echo \"Agentd binary failed\" && exit 1)\n\t@docker run --rm $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-agentd picod --help > /dev/null || (echo \"Picod binary failed\" && exit 1)\n\t@echo \"All images validated\"\n\n# ==============================================================================\n# Cleanup Targets\n# ==============================================================================\n\n.PHONY: docker-clean\n\ndocker-clean:\n\tdocker rmi $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-router:$(DOCKER_TAG) $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-router:latest 2>/dev/null || true\n\tdocker rmi $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-workload-manager:$(DOCKER_TAG) $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-workload-manager:latest 2>/dev/null || true\n\tdocker rmi $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-agentd:$(DOCKER_TAG) $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)-agentd:latest 2>/dev/null || true","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/Makefile"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler_test.go\">\nERROR [146:6] expected '(', found TestGetObservedGenerationCodeInterpreter\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/workloadmanager/expiration_test.go\">\nERROR [94:16] undefined: metav1\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go\">\nERROR [15:2] \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/watch\" imported and not used\nERROR [66:14] cannot use &metav1.Status{…} (value of type *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status) as error value in return statement: *\"k8s.io/api