stage to `/usr/local/bin/router`\n- [x] **T015** Set correct file permissions (chmod +x)\n- [x] **T016** Configure ENTRYPOINT for router binary\n- [ ] **T017** Verify `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-router:test .` succeeds\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: Workload Manager Dockerfile\n\n- [ ] **T020** Create `docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager` with multi-stage build\n- [ ] **T021** Builder stage builds workload-manager binary from `cmd/workload-manager/main.go`\n- [ ] **T022** Runtime stage uses `alpine:3.19` as base\n- [ ] **T023** Create non-root user `agentcube` (UID 1000)\n- [ ] **T024** Copy binary from builder stage to `/usr/local/bin/workload-manager`\n- [ ] **T025** Set correct file permissions (chmod +x)\n- [ ] **T026** Configure ENTRYPOINT for workload-manager binary\n- [ ] **T027** Verify `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager -t agentcube-workload-manager:test .` succeeds\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Agentd Dockerfile\n\n- [ ] **T030** Create `docker/Dockerfile.agentd` with multi-stage build\n- [ ] **T031** Builder stage builds agentd binary from `cmd/agentd/main.go`\n- [ ] **T032** Builder stage builds picod binary from `cmd/picod/main.go`\n- [ ] **T033** Runtime stage uses `alpine:3.19` as base\n- [ ] **T034** Create non-root user `agentcube` (UID 1000)\n- [ ] **T035** Copy both binaries from builder stage to `/usr/local/bin/`\n- [ ] **T036** Set correct file permissions (chmod +x)\n- [ ] **T037** Configure ENTRYPOINT for agentd binary (supports picod as argument)\n- [ ] **T038** Verify `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.agentd -t agentcube-agentd:test .` succeeds\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Binary Execution Verification\n\n- [ ] **T040** Test router binary: `docker run --rm agentcube-router:test --help` exits 0\n- [ ] **T041** Test workload-manager binary: `docker run --rm agentcube-workload-manager:test --help` exits 0\n- [ ] **T042** Test agentd binary: `docker run --rm agentcube-agentd:test --help` exits 0\n- [ ] **T043** Test picod binary: `docker run --rm agentcube-agentd:test picod --help` exits 0\n- [ ] **T044** Test router version: `docker run --rm agentcube-router:test version` exits 0\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: Security Verification\n\n- [ ] **T050** Verify router runs as non-root: `docker run --rm agentcube-router:id` shows uid=1000\n- [ ] **T051** Verify workload-manager runs as non-root: `docker run --rm agentcube-workload-manager:id` shows uid=1000\n- [ ] **T052** Verify agentd runs as non-root: `docker run --rm agentcube-agentd:id` shows uid=1000\n- [ ] **T053** Verify no source code in router: `docker run --rm agentcube-router ls /build` returns error\n- [ ] **T054** Verify no go.mod in router: `docker run --rm agentcube-router cat go.mod` returns error\n\n---\n\n## Phase 7: Image Size Verification\n\n- [ ] **T060** Check router image size: `docker images agentcube-router --format \"{{.Size}}\"` < 50MB\n- [ ] **T061** Check workload-manager image size: `docker images agentcube-workload-manager --format \"{{.Size}}\"` < 50MB\n- [ ] **T062** Check agentd image size: `docker images agentcube-agentd --format \"{{.Size}}\"` < 60MB\n\n---\n\n## Phase 8: Makefile Integration (Optional)\n\n- [ ] **T070** Add docker-build-router target to Makefile\n- [ ] **T071** Add docker-build-workload-manager target to Makefile\n- [ ] **T072** Add docker-build-agentd target to Makefile\n- [ ] **T073** Add docker-build (all) target to Makefile\n- [ ] **T074** Verify `make docker-build-router` succeeds\n\n---\n\n## Phase 9: Cache Reuse Verification\n\n- [ ] **T080** Run first build (cold): `time docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-router:test .`\n- [ ] **T081** Run second build (no changes): `time docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-router:test .`\n- [ ] **T082** Verify second build completes in < 30 seconds (cache reused)\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n```\nT001 → T002 → T003 → T004\nT010-T017 (Router - depends on T002-T004)\nT020-T027 (Workload Manager - depends on T002-T004)\n